'''Christopher Sheldrake''' is a [[perfumer]]. He has created perfumes for [[Shiseido]], [[Serge Lutens]], [[Rochas]], [[Avon Products, Inc.|Avon]] and [[SpaceNK]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.basenotes.net/fragrancedirectory/?search=Sheldrake |title=Sheldrake search results |work=Basenotes |accessdate=February 25, 2012}}</ref>

