===Republic of Ireland=== There are 187 stone circles in the [[Republic of Ireland]]. The vast majority of these are in [[County Cork]], which has 103 circles. There are 20 circles in [[County Kerry]] and 11 in [[County Mayo]].<ref name=":0" />
